{
  "id": "adv_main_01_07_01",
  "title": "星見編2章21話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は月ストが、星見市の文化交流イベント）\n（『星見カルチャーフェスティバル』に参加する日だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Today is the day of the Hoshimi Culture Festival‚)\n(and Moon Tempest is going to be performing there.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.41655818114044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "今日はこのステージに呼んでいただいて\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you all for coming out today\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.343976447164348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私達月のテンペストは\nまだデビューしたばかりの新しいグループです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are Moon Tempest‚\na new idol group that has just debuted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.799891419106345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 16.945650969836734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "よろしければ、この月のテンペストという\n名前だけでも覚えていって下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If possible‚ we hope that you at least remember\nthe name‚ Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4910232788403,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2375.6433878263683,
          "startTime": 21.866666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 22.134494696948558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "知ってるよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.13449469694856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 24.023542319629225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、知ってる人いた！\nありがとー！　もっと頑張るからねー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! We’ve got a fan out there!\nThanks! We’ll keep doing better and better for you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.556875652962553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 31.056875652962553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "私達のことを知らなかった方々も\nこの曲で虜にしてあげますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This next song will captivate\neven those of you who aren’t our fans yet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8902089862959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 36.62354231962923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "それでは聴いてください！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please listen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.62354231962923,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3200.0000000000027,
          "startTime": 39.82354231962923
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 39.12354231962923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "――ご……ご声援ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-Thank you for your support!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.42354231962923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 44.20753317961458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob2",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すずにゃんかわいいよおおおおっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ you’re so cuuute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.20753317961458,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2.1316282072803006e-11,
          "startTime": 44.2075331796146
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "へ？\nその呼び方、定着してるんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha?\nIs that an established nickname of mine?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.32381438701714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 51.14048105368376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "――ご声援、感謝いたしますわ！\n私に目をつけるなんて、なかにゃか……やりますわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your support!\nYou’ve got great taste‚ since you’re kitten… er‚ smitten with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.00714772035047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん！　噛んでますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu! You’re slurring your words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.29025416661664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 61.913428833975004
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うぉおおおおおおおおっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oooh!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.91342883397504,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 61.71342883397504
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういうところもかわいいよぉおおおお！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re so cute when you’re like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.41342883397504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 67.64676207367937
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 67.74676216730838
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 68.08009550064169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、お疲れ様\nいいステージだったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ girls.\nThat was a great performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.98009550064167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 72.58009550064168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "最後のすずにゃんのレスポンス\nお客さんにウケてたね！　噛んだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ that response you gave at the end\nreally got the crowd going! Even though you messed up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.68009550064167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 76.51342883397501
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 77.74458243493437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "すずの自信満々なパフォーマンスには\n見習うべきところがあるわね。噛んだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu’s confident performance style has\nsomething we can all learn from. Even though she did mess up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.64458243493435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 83.07791576826769
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 84.37895075921413
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "それ、引っ張らないでくださいます！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can you please stop bringing that up?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.37895075921413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは。でも、そこも含めてウケてたよね\nすずちゃん、すごいな。私ももっと頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ but you messing up your words was part of why they loved you.\nYou sure are amazing‚ Suzu. I need to up my game.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.30511846983627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 96.40511846983627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。あんな強気なセリフを堂々と言えるのは\n私達の中ではすずちゃんだけだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I think the only person among us who could say such a bold line\nwould be you‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.17178513650292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 103.3051184698364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私達はここから駆け上がっていくグループですのよ？\nならば、声援を送ってくれている方々は大正解",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we are an up-and-coming group‚ are we not?\nIn that case‚ the ones who cheer the loudest for us are correct.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.73845180316972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
      "startTime": 112.27764743610432
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "自分達に先見の明があったのだと思わせてあげるのが\n私達の使命であり、声援に対する回答ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Making them think they’re prophets who discovered us\nis not only our duty; it is our answer to their cheering!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.37764743610438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stgae02",
